 a multivariate factor stochastic volatility\nmodel proposed by Kastner et al(2017). Our proposed approach shows superior\nperformance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Aug 2018 21:24:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jul 2019 13:06:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-22"}
