erms of 3 phase shifts and 3\nin-elasticity parameters, as one would expect from the coupled-channel\nunitarity condition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Aug 2018 05:57:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 Feb 2023 05:29:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-21"}
